thread.title: Mike Gregus

author: Mike Gregus
title: Mike Gregus
text:
Incredible Keepsakes would like to thank all the Anajet personal that worked diligently to get us backup and running smoothly. We understand
the process of locating the source of the problem sometimes can make
a person upset. The team of Techs and Engineers we worked with were amazing. We would also like to thank Juan for his trip to Ohio and made sure our mP5 was properly functioning. Anajet's Customer Service made us believers. We feel they went the extra distance and stand behind their products. Incredible Keepsakes is proud to be part the Anajet Industry.
